# Simple Stakeholder Register

**Project:** [Project Name]  
**Updated:** [Date]  
**Owner:** [Project Manager Name]  

## Why This Matters
Knowing your stakeholders and their needs is critical to project success. This simple register helps you:
- Identify who has influence over your project
- Understand what each person cares about
- Plan appropriate communication strategies
- Avoid surprises from unhappy stakeholders

