**Strategy:** Monitor and inform occasionally

## Communication Plan Summary

| Stakeholder Type | Communication Method | Frequency | Content Focus |
|------------------|---------------------|-----------|---------------|
| Champions | Face-to-face meetings | Weekly | Detailed progress, decisions needed |
| Blockers | Executive summaries | Bi-weekly | High-level status, risk mitigation |
| Supporters | Email updates | Weekly | Progress updates, ways to help |
| Monitor | Mass emails | Monthly | General project status |

## Red Flags to Watch For üö©

- [ ] **Stakeholder not responding** to communications
- [ ] **New requirements** being added by stakeholders
- [ ] **Conflicting priorities** between stakeholders
- [ ] **Scope creep** requests from influential stakeholders
- [ ] **Budget concerns** being raised quietly
- [ ] **Political issues** between stakeholders

