## Quick Reference: Stakeholder Management Tips

### üöÄ Do This
- Meet with high-influence stakeholders early and often
- Ask what success looks like to each stakeholder
- Understand their communication preferences
- Address concerns before they become problems
- Keep promises you make to stakeholders

### üö´ Avoid This
- Assuming all stakeholders want the same thing
- Over-communicating to low-interest stakeholders
- Under-communicating to high-influence stakeholders
- Making promises you can't keep
- Ignoring stakeholder politics

